(91, 91, 1, 'AdIns dan BCA mengadakan Campus Hiring di STTS', 'AdIns Center of Excellence (ACE) sedang mencari lulusan S1 bidang Teknologi Informatika (Ilmu Komputer/Teknik Informatika/Sistem Informasi) yang bersedia mengikuti training <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Java Developer (GRATIS)</span>, untuk selanjutnya ditempatkan sebagai <span style=\"font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;\">karyawan tetap</span> di Divisi teknologi Informasi PT Bank Central Asia Tbk (BCA).<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;\">Syarat:</span><br><ol><li>Mahasiswa tingkat akhir/lulusan S1 bidang Teknologi Informatika (Ilmu Komputer/Teknik Informatika/Sistem \nInformasi);</li><li>IP kumulatif minimal 3.00;</li><li>Usia max. 25 tahun;</li><li>Menyukai dunia TI, khususnya bidang pemrograman;</li><li>Bersedia mengikuti pelatihan dan penempatan kerja di Jakarta;</li><li>Bersedia mengikuti proses seleksi (teknis, psikotes, wawancara).</li></ol><br>Ikuti penjelasan dan tes seleksi teknis ACE yang akan diadakan pada:<br>Hari/Tanggal&nbsp; : Selasa, 30 Maret 2010<br>Waktu&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Pukul 09.30-15.00 WIB<br>Tempat&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Ruang L-407<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Gedung Laboratorium Lt. 4<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Sekolah Tinggi Teknik Surabaya<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Jl. Ngagel Jaya Tengah 73-77<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Surabaya<br><br>Pada hari pelaksanaan acara harap membawa:<br><ol><li>2 lembar FC transkrip nilai terakhir</li><li>2 lembar pas foto berwarna</li></ol>Isi dan kembalikan formulir pendaftaran ke:<br>Ruang L-202<br>Sekolah Tinggi Teknik Surabaya<br>Telp. (031) 502 1252 / 502 7920 (Sdri. Ika)<br><br>Info lebih lanjut hubungi:<br>joana.amdanni@ad-ins.com / (021) 5367 3030 ext. 4521<br><br><br>'),
(92, 92, 1, 'SAP Education Day in STTS', '<p>Surabaya is second largest city in Indonesia with high potential in \neconomic and business growth especially for east Indonesia. There are \nalso many big companies using SAP as business software, which need SAP \neducation for developing their internal team and inquiries of SAP \nresources.&nbsp; Here Monsoon Academy will held SAP Education Day in \nSurabaya.&nbsp; Detail as follows: 1st April and 5th April, location: STTS \ncampus. We will open on 10.00 a.m to 15.00 p.m.&nbsp; So anytime you can \nvisit us during the open hour.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p><p>SAP Education Day will consist of:</p><p>- Grand Open session</p><p>-\n Free Trial of&nbsp; eAcademy </p><p>- Pre Hired Program for Fresh Graduates</p><p><strong><br></strong></p><p><strong>Get\n special Promo of Highly Potential Fresh Graduates </strong>in this \nevent!</p><br><p>See You there! <br></p><p><br></p><p>Contact Person:</p><p>Fransisca Yunita</p><p>Ph. (031) 70022484</p><p>email: surabaya@monsoonacademy.com</p>'),
