(102, 102, 1, 'CAMPUS HIRING', '<br><div style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: bold;\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\" size=\"5\">PT SAYAP MAS UTAMA</font><br><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">As one of the largest producers of consumer goods in Indonesia.</span><br style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Now, They give you an opportunity to join us and be a valuable person with fill these position</span><br><font size=\"4\"><br>PROGRAMMER<br>APPLICATION SUPPORT<br>IT OPERATIONAL<br>DATABASE ADMINISTRATOR<br>DISTRIBUTION CENTER CONTROLLER<br>INTERNATIONAL BUSINESS<br>SUPPLY CHAIN MANAGEMENT<br>IT NETWORKING<br>PRODUCTION</font><br><font size=\"4\"><br></font></font><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><font size=\"3\"><font size=\"4\">General Requirement:</font></font><br></div><ul style=\"font-weight: normal; text-align: left;\"><li><font size=\"3\">Minimum GPA 3.00 <br></font></li><li><font size=\"3\">Having good command English</font></li><li><font size=\"3\">Having good communication <br></font></li><li><font size=\"3\">Interpersonal skill</font></li><li><font size=\"3\">Team coordination skill</font></li><li><font size=\"3\">Leadership skill</font></li><li><font size=\"3\">Analysis ability</font></li><li><font size=\"3\">Computer skill</font></li><li><font size=\"3\">Dynamic</font></li><li><font size=\"3\">Creative</font></li><li><font size=\"3\">Tough and fast learner</font></li></ul><br><font size=\"4\">Please send your complete application, curriculum vitae, and recent photograph to Ibu Ika (Bagian Kemahasiswaan) before October 5, 2010</font><br><br><br><font size=\"4\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 0);\">COME to OUR PRESENTATION &amp; SELECTION TEST:</span><br>TUESDAY 05th, 2010<br>09.00 am<br>at L-407 Room</font><br><br><br><br><br><br></div></div>'),
(103, 103, 1, 'Pendaftaran S1 Informatika Kelas Malam 2010-2011', '<font size=\"3\">Program S1 Informatika Kelas Malam, Kesempatan unik untuk mengembangkan Karir dan Melanjutkan studi secara bersamaan<br><br>Keistimewaan jurusan:<br>1.&nbsp; Konsentrasi: Enterprise Information System<br>2.&nbsp; Tenaga pengajar berpengalaman<br>3.&nbsp; Satu komputer untuk satu mahasiswa <br>4.&nbsp; Kelas kecil untuk kualitas kuliah terbaik<br>5.&nbsp; Fasilitas koneksi WiFi<br>6.&nbsp; Lingkungan kampus yang asri<br>7.&nbsp; Opsi studi lanjut S2 di Swinburne, Australia.<br><br>Untuk informasi lebih lengkap, kunjungi:<br>http://www.stts.edu/pendidikan/s1inforKelasMalam.htm</font><br>'),
(104, 104, 1, 'How To Become An Expert In C. Report', 'Ikuti Workshop \"<font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">How To Become An Expert In Crystal Report</span></font>\" dengan pembicara Stefanus Christofan, yang dibagi menjadi 3 (tiga) tiga tahap selama 3 (tiga) hari. <br>\n<br>\n<ol></ol>\n<ul style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><li><font size=\"3\">Basic Level of Crystal Report</font></li></ul>\n<div style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Sabtu, 23 Oktober 2010 pk. 09.00 - 11.00 WIB di L-304</span><br>\n</div>\n<ol></ol>\n<ul style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><li><font size=\"3\">Connecting Crystal Report with Microsoft Visual Studio</font></li></ul>\n<div style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Sabtu, 30 Oktober 2010 pk. 09.00 - 11.00 WIB di L-304</span><br>\n</div>\n<br>\n<ul style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><li><font size=\"3\">Advanced Level of Crystal Report</font></li></ul>\n<div style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Sabtu, 06 November 2010 pk. 09.00 - 11.00 WIB di L-304</span><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n</div>\nSegera daftarkan diri kamu untuk mengikuti workshop ini dan kamu akan tidak akan kesulitan lagi untuk membuat sebuah laporan.<br>\nUntuk pendaftaran, dapat melalui : - <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Indra Maryati, S.Kom., BAA lt.2 (081 703 207 992)</span><br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">BAA lt.1</span><br>\n<br>\n<hr style=\"width: 100%; height: 2px;\"><font size=\"1\">* Jumlah peserta dibatasi hanya <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">35 orang</span><br>\n* Terbuka untuk <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">semua jurusan</span><br>\n* Akan diberikan sertifikat dan poin kegiatan kemahasiswaan<br>\n* Diharapkan para peserta sudah menguasai bahasa pemrograman V