(304, 304, 1, 'Start Surabaya Goes to Campus', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\">Mau tahu seperti apa dunia Startup itu? Atau punya mimpi ke Silicon Valley, pusat startup dunia dan markas perusahaan teknologi terkenal seperti Facebook dan Google?</span><br style=\"color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\" />\r\n	<br style=\"color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\" />\r\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\">Ayo ikuti START SURABAYA GOES TO CAMPUS. Di sini, kalian bisa tahu apa saja ilmu yang didapatkan para startup selama mengunjungi Silicon Valley.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\" />\r\n	<br style=\"color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\" />\r\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\">Acara diadakan pada Jumat, 11 Maret 2016 di kampus iSTTS.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\" />\r\n	<br style=\"color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\" />\r\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\">Daftar sekarang juga di&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://bit.ly/DelihomeSTTS\" rel=\"nofollow nofollow\" style=\"color: rgb(59, 89, 152); cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/DelihomeSTTS</a></p